title: Clean Disk Security v8 04-BEAN
description:
Clean Disk Security v8.04 (C) Kevin Solway

Disks: 2 x 2,88mb Date: August 26, 2013
OS: Windows Type: Reg File

Release Description:

Clean Disk Security gives you secure file deletion, ensuring that
deleted files cannot be undeleted again. Deleting a file normally just
removes the file's directory entry, but the data itself remains on the
disk. This program completely eliminates the contents of deleted files
The highly acclaimed Gutmann disk cleaning method is now available as an
option. This program also removes the tracks of Internet browsing
cleans the Window's swap file, cleans unneeded temporary files from your
hard disk, as well as files in your system's Recycle Bin, and can clear
the "recent files" list. The included plugins clean up after all manner
of applications

Installation:
"""""""""""""""

Just unpack install. Execute bean.reg
